      • testDeleteConstraintThenSlackVariable

        public void testDeleteConstraintThenSlackVariable()
        Tests that the dualizer can correctly handle deleting a slack variable if the corresponding linear constraint has already been deleted. Creates a conic program with an inequality constraint, checks out the dual program, checks it back in, then deletes first the constraint and second the slack variable.
